85. Oh boy, today the sun is so hot! We went hunting\'97we\'92re exhausted.\
86. Woman: You men go hunting, we women catch frogs.\
87. H: I didn\'92t get to shoot a single animal. Nobody drove any animals towards me.\
88. Down below there you should have followed the animals\'92 trail properly. There were plenty [25] of barking-deer tracks.\
